\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Shift + any mouse button sets the volume and balance sliders back to 0 dB
 and Center position, respectively.
 This combination also works for the loop bar, in which case the looping
 range is set to the whole song.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
