, but you may specify another server (maybe a close mirror).
 The connection timeout can also be set here.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If you want to update or submit records to the CDDB server, you will have
 to give a valid email address.
 Should your submission be rejected for some reason, you will receive a
 note about the failure to this address.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Instead of connecting directly to the CDDB server you can use an HTTP proxy.
 This case you have to specify the proxy server address and port (the protocol
 will be HTTP).
\end_layout

